OL,5, UK billionaire Joe Lewis, whose family 
OL,6, trust owns Tottenham Hotspur football  
OL,7, club, has pleaded guilty to insider    
OL,8, trading in a US court.                 
OL,10,FLewis, 86, was accused of passing on   
OL,11,Finformation about his companies to his 
OL,12,Fprivate pilots, friends, personal      
OL,13,Fassistants and romantic partners.      
OL,15,FUS authorities say that the fraud      
OL,16,Fnetted millions of dollars in profit.  
OL,18,FLewis pleaded guilty to conspiracy and 
OL,19,Ftwo counts of securities fraud as part 
OL,20,Fof a deal with prosecutors.            
